name: Gypsy Heart Mintpass by Violetta Zironi

metadata.name: Gypsy Heart Mintpass
metadata.description:
My second NFT album, the follow up collection to Moonshot, is coming at the end of January 2023. Another 5 original songs, this time each paired with a collection of 5K hand drawn PFPs inspired by the music. The public mint will be 0.1 ETH.

The songs are all recorded analog, on tape, and will be minted on the Ethereum blockchain, where they will live forever.

You now have the opportunity to pre purchase your NFT before the official mint starts by buying the Gypsy Heart Mintpass for 0.08 ETH (20% discount from the public mint price of 0.1).

This is the lowest entry price there will ever be for the Gypsy Heart collection, and there are only 500 available.

Every mint pass will equal 1 NFT claim.Holding a mint pass will also grant you access to the allowlist mint, which will be cheaper than 0.1, but still more than 0.08.

Before the official presale starts, we will take a snapshot. When presale begins, youâ€™ll be able to claim your Gypsy Heart NFT from that same wallet.
